Refactor scheduling, update configurations, and align ports
Introduced a `SchedulingConfig` class for better management of scheduling properties. Updated the `TaskProcessor` to use the new configuration and resolved minor formatting issues in `CoderExecutionService`. Additionally, the Java toolchain was configured to use Java 17, and the default application port was aligned to `8080`.
.idea-specific files updated and new Gradle and Docker configurations added for enhanced project build, deployment, and testing settings.
